Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:15.07,info,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\q2\move(2350,10,-2000,10,0,15000)\b0\blur3}本片由千夏字幕組製作 論壇：http://www.airota.net 翻譯：銀月 Kentei 小哈  校對：小哈  時間軸：阿卡林  繁化：筒隱月子  後期：騎士 321
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}乖乖 金剛二號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.36,0:00:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你還真是喜歡西瓜皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這麼熱的天你去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真虧你每天看著還不膩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}每天…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.68,0:00:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}糟糕了千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.25,0:01:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我想到了一件不得了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.05,0:01:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}暑假還剩下一周就要結束了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這種事情早就發現了！ 蠢蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這個夏天不是還有什麼事情沒有做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是說你那從暑假開始以來就一直遭到放置PLAY的暑假作業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.82,0:01:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.76,0:01:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你的暑假作業肯定做完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}暑假剛剛開始就立刻把作業一本不剩地做完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:36.74,Title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\pos(496,366)}{\frz23.244\pos(262,236)\fs40\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}個人目標  翻單杠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不說作業的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}千秋 要說到我們夏天還沒做的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大海！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}內田
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}說到蔚藍的大海會想到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}蔚藍的天空！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.06,0:01:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}說到蔚藍的天空呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:01:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太陽！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}說到太陽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這樣啊 都到宇宙去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}天涯海角勇往直前!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}明明都到八月下旬了 真是來海邊的好天氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大海在等著我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎麼了千秋 我們今年夏天還沒來過的海邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我先去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}為什麼情緒這麼低落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不 也不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不太會游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要下海需要相當大的決心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以現在正在集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你一臉糾結的樣子別人會擔心的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這樣可不好 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}先從形式上下手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你要把正準備享受大海的心情表現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這樣看上去就像是正準備享受大海了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是呢 那麼接下來集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你在幹什麼啊千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你這樣一個正準備享受大海的人站在沙灘上可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}趕緊飛身躍入海裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}放開我 我還沒做好心理準備…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夏奈 我被誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看來我外表和內心的反差很大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這下頭疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那就把還不想去海裏玩的心情表現出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好好 只要穿好衣服坐著…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喂 千秋 你在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}快把這衣服脫了 去海裏玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不不不不不…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}反而讓她們更加擔心 立馬就被扒掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不好辦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對了 集中精神的話你應該擺一個相應的POSE才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夏奈 我是不是被盯著了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}估計是好奇你在幹什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}視線擾亂著我的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這樣就不能集中精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我陪她們三個去玩 你快下定決心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}千秋不去海裏玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}春香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我過一會就去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那我先去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不快點的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一個人決定下海的POSE！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真是的 很咸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那吃點甜的東西中和一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我想吃刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}贊成！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那先上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}刨冰！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}千秋要不要一起去吃刨冰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}贊成吃刨冰的POSE…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}春香 你那是什麼POSE啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}吃刨冰吃得頭疼的POSE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}肚子飽了的POSE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}討厭你的POSE？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不 只是想讓你們看看舌頭是不是被糖漿染色了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是不是討厭 答案先保留吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你說喜歡也沒關係的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道了 想再來一份的POSE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果作業也做完了那該多好的POSE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不要說作業的事情的POSE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什麼啊 你們幾個還沒寫完作業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我家的千秋早就做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真厲害啊千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}已經全部做完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}個人目標也完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}個人目標？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我記得千秋的個人目標好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\frz353.874\pos(568,506)}{\fad(200,0)\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fn方正汉真广标简体}個人目標 翻單杠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}翻單杠…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}做不完
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只剩下三天了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看來只能想點對策了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}都怪你自己因為夏天要結束了就拚命地玩 蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那你又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}會翻單杠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}翻單杠還不會的話 就不能說暑假作業做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}千秋 能幫我去買點東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好的 春香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我去吧 偶爾也轉換一下心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}轉換心情？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}等你專心寫過一次作業再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}拜託了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}歡迎回來 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎麼了千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喂 千秋 你把我的金剛二號弄哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}咦 我什麼都沒做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是它自己逃跑的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那你是說金剛二號自己打開蓋子出去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我可沒教過它這種玩意兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我才不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是對每天只給西瓜皮的你感到不耐煩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}現在應該是被某個富裕家庭收養
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}正在吃著蜜瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我也時不時在西瓜皮上塗點刨冰的蜜瓜糖漿給它的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}金剛二號想逃離此處的心情我真是感同身受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}金剛二號你到底去哪裏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}千秋 這罪過很深重哦 再也不跟你講話了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什麼 還在懷疑我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喂喂 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因為它不可能自己逃出去的吧 它可是獨角僊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夏奈 千秋 別吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}春香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}金剛二號…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夏奈 真的不是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎麼了 千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是我放跑它的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那黑乎乎的是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抓到一隻獨角僊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}吶 可以養咱家裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不行 你玩膩了誰來照顧它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我才不會玩膩 連名字都想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夏樹 你也想待在這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你在朝哪邊講話 我可在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對了 夏樹 你肚子餓不餓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對了 我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}今天的點心是別人送的蜜瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊咧 我的蜜瓜少了一塊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那一塊在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎麼回事 為什麼會在你那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這是那只獨角僊的份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要飼養動物 就要把自己的食物分給…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我本來就是這麼打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夏樹 好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大家好啊 我過來玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}哦 小真啊 你還真是從容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這種時候還能出來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}作業當然已經做完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}作業？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:11:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒做完嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不要因為在做暑假作業就覺得了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}咦 不是 我並沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你肯定認為我這種人做不了作業的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你走著瞧 我也是被別人誇讚過「認真干就能成功」的孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那傢伙是來幹啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夏奈 那裏的答案也太胡猜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}咦 那景子的答案是正確的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大概
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你既然都這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那就讓我用這雙慧眼鑒別一下你的答案正確與否吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夏奈 想讓別人給你看的話就好好求一下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}請給我看一下拜託了的POSE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真是拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不能寵著夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:12:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}作業已經做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}當然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}別被騙了哦 藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那傢伙作業還有剩的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}還是不要理這種拖後腿的傢伙比較好哦 藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}藤岡 我可是被別人誇讚過「認真干就能成功」的孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是… 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}認真干肯定能成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對吧 有什麼不明白的就來問能幹的我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我會充滿自信地回答你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那 我想問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這裏面有什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}現在在我心中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}踩地雷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其它的問題我都能回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}比起那個還是先做作業吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}春香沒什麼精神啊 苦夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}覺得最近夏奈和千秋都沒啥精神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那些孩子感覺吃點好吃的就會瞬間變得精神起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 這個冰淇淋看上去好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果世上所有人都像真希學姐這樣單純就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好吃的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}篤子學姐 還沒決定要點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊咧 一不留神夏樹不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}逃走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}蓋子沒合上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不會是討厭那個狹小的盒子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夏樹 珍重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}吵死了 我珍重得很
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是說你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:15:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我覺得再稍微把鐵棒貼近身體一點比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}手開始疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要不今天就到這吧 你很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可是暑假明天就要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒事的 還差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}明天一定能成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夏奈 還在睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你是金剛二號嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是金剛二號吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我學會翻單杠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好厲害啊 千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真想讓你們看看我那鯉魚躍龍門般的英姿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}金剛二號？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抱歉 千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是你放走的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}哦 現在我有作為成功人士的從容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不用放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對了千秋 剛才你是不是說可以翻單杠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯 沒能給你看真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好 既然這樣就再去公園翻給我看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小菜一碟 蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}已經成功過一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}肯定有第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}等著看我鮭魚躍龍門般的英姿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}雖然我也想去看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但還是做慶祝的準備呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}咦 慶祝？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好 因為可以翻單杠了所以要開派對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不用那麼當回事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夏奈 帶上相機哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}包在我身上 春香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}今天會成為翻單杠紀念日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}紀…紀念日也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}每年的今天把千秋的朋友邀請過來開一個盛大的派對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}別啊 丟死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}變得麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}來 讓我看看你那如蛟龍出海般的英姿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}吶 夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果我現在沒能做到翻單杠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我就會被認為是騙子 慶祝會也泡湯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是當然 今天的晚飯就會變得極為儉樸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是說我的晚飯也會變得極為儉樸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}別問我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}千秋 絕對要成功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你一定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一次就能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一次？ 這哪來的鬼規則
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一次哦 千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.23,0:18:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一切就看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你一定能做到 我相信你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}千秋 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太好了呢 千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}翻單杠紀念日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}派對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}恭喜你 你很努力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}恭喜你 這是特等壽司哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}千秋 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}呃 失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}當然 派對中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是菜都準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因為那異常的壓力…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真是不抗壓的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我做到了的 按照藤岡的方法試了試結果做到了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你今天是在夢裏成功的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}別這樣 我會當真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}至少請再給我一次機會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}下次一定能成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以晚飯就當是提前慶祝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}原來如此 這想法不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}吃了美味的飯菜 力量湧上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}感覺現在能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎麼了 千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}肚子太沉翻不上去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.13,0:20:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好 來慢跑助消化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}走好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎麼了 千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太累翻不上去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}先休息會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}到頭來還是沒成為翻單杠紀念日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是成為了和好紀念日 不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}明天能成功就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然後明天也吃大餐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.19,0:24:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果世上所有人都像真希學姐這樣單純就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.51,0:24:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.25,0:24:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}篤子學姐 還沒決定要點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.10,0:24:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.24,0:24:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}篤子可是相當的優柔寡斷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.30,0:24:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}基本上都是跟我或者春香點一樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.70,0:24:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.95,0:24:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這樣可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.79,0:24:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要按照自己的意願決定啊 果斷地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.62,0:24:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯… 必須自己決定才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.92,0:24:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好啦好啦 瞳 別老是催她
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.19,0:24:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很在意她們倆會點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.04,0:24:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這樣的話 還會總是關注著她們倆的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.35,0:24:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果被她們的男朋友求愛了…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.96,0:24:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}「咦 也挺好的 雖然是不好的事情 但好像也挺好的」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.80,0:24:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很可能會發展成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.73,0:24:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎麼會啦 那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.79,0:24:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嘛 雖然現在還沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.62,0:24:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不好意思 可以點單嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.41,0:24:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}咦 我還沒定好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.42,0:25:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在服務員過來之前定下來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.46,0:25:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}咦 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.83,0:25:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}還剩5米哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.83,0:25:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}還剩4米
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.35,0:25:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}3米
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.42,0:25:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}2米
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.54,0:25:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}1米
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.60,0:25:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.94,0:25:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}請給我這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.86,0:25:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}您要一份大號牛排套餐是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.37,0:25:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.88,0:25:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}飯量挺大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.77,0:25:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只是慌忙之下隨便指了一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.00,0:25:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}決定了…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.21,0:25:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}以自己的意願…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.07,0:25:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}瞳！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.02,0:25:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}篤子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.88,0:25:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這鬧哪樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.15,0:25:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但男人還是要當機立斷才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.93,0:25:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那忍耐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.79,0:25:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那個也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.68,0:25:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很深奧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.47,0:25:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那包容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.09,0:25:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那個也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.59,0:25:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}咦 篤子學姐 這和點的不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.00,0:26:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯 好像服務員搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.53,0:26:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是這樣也好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.54,0:26:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這樣可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.30,0:26:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要是這樣的話 被根本不喜歡的傢伙求愛了也不能拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.40,0:26:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}「咦 挺好的 雖然不是我想要的 但好像也挺好的」
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.25,0:26:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很可能會發展成這樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.36,0:26:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}服務員 不好意思過來下～
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.12,0:26:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.51,0:26:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.76,0:26:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}來 請果斷地說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.70,0:26:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊… 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.68,0:26:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那個…雖然這個也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.14,0:26:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}呃…這樣也非常好…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.01,0:26:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.88,0:26:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我要的是大號牛排套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.96,0:26:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我想吃牛排套餐！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.86,0:27:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}瞳！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.01,0:27:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}篤子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.16,0:27:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.17,0:27:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.91,0:27:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這是我自己決定的…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.64,0:27:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好的 請問您要帶什麼飲料？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.41,0:27:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可樂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.12,0:27:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.45,0:27:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}還是要可樂

